related_questions.question: Is indeed a good job search site?
related_questions.snippet: Some of the best job sites are traditional job boards, like Monster, Dice, and CareerBuilder. Others, like Indeed.com, allow you to search through many job boards, company career sites, associations, and other sources of job postings. You can even search directly on Google to find job opportunities.

related_questions.question: How much does indeed cost?
related_questions.snippet: The cost of posting a job on Indeed starts at $0.00. Pricing is between $0.10 and $5.00 per click if you boost your post with a pay-per-click campaign.Jul 30, 2019
